---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Market Landscape — Global + HK">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-12">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Market Landscape</span><span class="lang-zh">市場動態</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">Market Landscape</span><span class="lang-zh">市場動態</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-3xl">
      <span class="lang-en">The world's largest financial institutions are building onchain infrastructure. Hong Kong's government and regulators are actively pushing forward. Here is the latest landscape.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">全球最大嘅金融機構已經喺度建onchain infrastructure。香港政府同金融監管機構都積極推進。呢度係最新嘅landscape。</span>
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Global Section -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
      <span class="lang-en">Global — Major Institutional Moves</span><span class="lang-zh">全球 — 大行動態</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">BlackRock, JP Morgan, Goldman Sachs, NYSE, Citadel, Jane Street — all in.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">BlackRock、JP Morgan、Goldman Sachs、NYSE、Citadel、Jane Street — 全部已經入場。</span>
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- BlackRock -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">BlackRock BUIDL</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
            <span class="lang-en">Asset Management</span><span class="lang-zh">資產管理</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Tokenized US Treasuries fund — real T-bills onchain.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">Tokenized US Treasuries fund — 真正嘅T-bills onchain。</span>
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">AUM:</span> $2.9B</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Chains:</span> <span class="lang-en">9 (Ethereum, Solana, Avalanche, etc.)</span><span class="lang-zh">9條（Ethereum、Solana、Avalanche等）</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Notable:</span> <span class="lang-en">Binance accepts BUIDL as collateral — a strong institutional adoption signal for onchain funds</span><span class="lang-zh">Binance接受BUIDL做collateral — onchain fund嘅institutional adoption signal</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- JP Morgan -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">JP Morgan Kinexys</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
            <span class="lang-en">Settlement</span><span class="lang-zh">結算</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Formerly Onyx — blockchain-based payment and settlement platform.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">前身 Onyx — blockchain-based payment同settlement platform。</span>
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Daily volume:</span><span class="lang-zh">日交易量：</span></span> $2B+ intraday repo</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Total processed:</span><span class="lang-zh">已處理總額：</span></span> $1.5T+</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Use case:</span><span class="lang-zh">應用場景：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Onchain FX settlement, intraday repo, cross-border payments</span><span class="lang-zh">Onchain FX settlement、intraday repo、cross-border payments</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Goldman Sachs -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Goldman Sachs GS DAP</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
            <span class="lang-en">Capital Markets</span><span class="lang-zh">資本市場</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Digital Asset Platform — private blockchain for bond issuance.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">Digital Asset Platform — private blockchain for bond issuance。</span>
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Notable deal:</span><span class="lang-zh">重要交易：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">EIB (European Investment Bank) EUR 100M digital bond</span><span class="lang-zh">EIB（歐洲投資銀行）EUR100M digital bond</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Roadmap:</span><span class="lang-zh">路線圖：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Plans to spin out as independent entity by mid-2026</span><span class="lang-zh">計劃mid-2026 spin out做獨立entity</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Implication:</span><span class="lang-zh">影響：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Investment banks using blockchain for primary issuance — beyond experiments</span><span class="lang-zh">投行開始用blockchain做primary issuance，唔止係experiment</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Citadel -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Citadel Securities</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
            <span class="lang-en">Market Making</span><span class="lang-zh">做市</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">The world's largest equities market maker, now expanding into crypto.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">全球最大equities market maker，開始做crypto。</span>
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Investment:</span><span class="lang-zh">投資：</span></span> $200M into Kraken</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Strategy:</span><span class="lang-zh">策略：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Expanding into crypto market-making</span><span class="lang-zh">擴展至crypto market-making</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Signal:</span><span class="lang-zh">信號：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">When Citadel enters crypto MM, liquidity depth will deepen significantly</span><span class="lang-zh">當Citadel入場做crypto MM，liquidity depth會大幅提升</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- NYSE -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">NYSE x Securitize</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
            <span class="lang-en">Exchange</span><span class="lang-zh">交易所</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">NYSE signed MOU with tokenization platform Securitize.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">NYSE同tokenization平台Securitize簽MOU。</span>
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Goal:</span><span class="lang-zh">目標：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">24/7 tokenized securities trading platform</span><span class="lang-zh">24/7代幣化證券交易平台</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Implication:</span><span class="lang-zh">影響：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Traditional stock exchanges embracing tokenized trading</span><span class="lang-zh">傳統stock exchange都開始embrace tokenized trading</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Jane Street -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Jane Street</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
            <span class="lang-en">Trading</span><span class="lang-zh">交易</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">One of the world's largest proprietary trading firms.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">全球最大proprietary trading firm之一。</span>
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">History:</span><span class="lang-zh">歷史：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Trading crypto since 2017</span><span class="lang-zh">2017年開始trading crypto</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Recent:</span><span class="lang-zh">近期：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Co-led Kraken's $800M funding round</span><span class="lang-zh">Co-led Kraken嘅$800M融資</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Signal:</span><span class="lang-zh">信號：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Quantitative trading giants deeply invested in crypto infrastructure</span><span class="lang-zh">量化交易巨頭深度佈局crypto infrastructure</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- DBS -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">DBS Singapore</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
            <span class="lang-en">Banking</span><span class="lang-zh">銀行</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Southeast Asia's largest bank, actively advancing digital assets.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">東南亞最大銀行，積極推進digital assets。</span>
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Products:</span><span class="lang-zh">產品：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Tokenized structured notes on Ethereum</span><span class="lang-zh">Ethereum上嘅代幣化結構性票據</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Trading:</span><span class="lang-zh">交易：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">$1B+ crypto options traded H1 2025</span><span class="lang-zh">2025年上半年交易超$1B crypto期權</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Signal:</span><span class="lang-zh">信號：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Asian banking leader with live crypto trading desk</span><span class="lang-zh">亞洲銀行leader已經有live crypto trading desk</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ICE -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">ICE (NYSE Parent)</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
            <span class="lang-en">Infrastructure</span><span class="lang-zh">基礎設施</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Intercontinental Exchange — parent company of NYSE and ICE Futures.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">Intercontinental Exchange — NYSE、ICE Futures嘅parent company。</span>
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Investment:</span><span class="lang-zh">投資：</span></span> $600M into Polymarket</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Signal:</span><span class="lang-zh">信號：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Exchange infrastructure giant sees prediction markets as next-generation information markets</span><span class="lang-zh">Exchange infrastructure巨頭認為prediction market = next generation information market</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HK Section -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
      <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong — Asia's Regulated Crypto Hub</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">香港 — 亞洲Regulated Crypto Hub</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Government, banks, and family offices are all moving.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">政府、銀行、家族辦公室全部都喺度move。</span>
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- Govt -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong Government</span><span class="lang-zh">香港政府</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Tokenized Green Bond:</span><span class="lang-zh">代幣化綠色債券：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">3rd issuance, cumulative HK$10B, settled via HSBC Orion</span><span class="lang-zh">第3次發行，累計HK$100億，HSBC Orion平台結算</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">VATP Licensing:</span> <span class="lang-en">12 platforms licensed (HashKey & OSL can serve retail)</span><span class="lang-zh">12間平台已獲牌照（HashKey、OSL可做retail）</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">SFC Staking:</span> <span class="lang-en">Greenlit staking in April 2025</span><span class="lang-zh">2025年4月greenlit staking</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">e-HKD:</span> <span class="lang-en">Pilot completed. Retail CBDC shelved, pivoting to wholesale + tokenized deposits</span><span class="lang-zh">Pilot completed，暫時唔搞retail CBDC，pivot去wholesale + tokenized deposits</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Family Office Tax:</span><span class="lang-zh">家族辦公室稅務：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Digital assets added to qualifying investments tax concession (Feb 2026)</span><span class="lang-zh">Digital assets列入qualifying investments稅務優惠（2026年2月）</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Banks -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">HSBC</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Tokenized deposits:</span><span class="lang-zh">代幣化存款：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Live, expanding globally</span><span class="lang-zh">已上線，全球擴展中</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Orion:</span> <span class="lang-en">Institutional tokenization platform, used for government green bond settlement</span><span class="lang-zh">Institutional tokenization platform，用於政府green bond結算</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Stablecoin:</span> <span class="lang-en">Among applicants for HK stablecoin license</span><span class="lang-zh">香港穩定幣牌照申請人之一</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Standard Chartered</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">First G-SIB:</span> <span class="lang-en">First global systemically important bank to offer spot crypto trading</span><span class="lang-zh">首間全球系統重要性銀行做spot crypto trading</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Partnership:</span> <span class="lang-en">HashKey banking partner</span><span class="lang-zh">HashKey銀行合作夥伴</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Stablecoin:</span> <span class="lang-en">HK stablecoin license applicant</span><span class="lang-zh">香港穩定幣牌照申請人</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Family Offices -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Family Offices</span><span class="lang-zh">家族辦公室</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">3,380+</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
              <span class="lang-en">HK family offices</span><span class="lang-zh">香港家族辦公室</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">52%</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
              <span class="lang-en">Plan crypto allocation</span><span class="lang-zh">計劃配置crypto</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">27%</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
              <span class="lang-en">Within 6 months</span><span class="lang-zh">6個月內行動</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400">Tax</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
              <span class="lang-en">Digital asset concessions</span><span class="lang-zh">Digital asset稅務優惠</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong has <span class="text-white font-medium">3,380+ family offices</span>. 52% plan crypto allocation, 27% within 6 months. From February 2026, digital assets qualify for tax concessions under the family office tax regime — a policy-level push for adoption.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">香港有 <span class="text-white font-medium">3,380+間family offices</span>，52%計劃配置crypto，27%會喺6個月內行動。2026年2月起digital assets列入qualifying investments享稅務優惠 — 呢個係政策層面嘅push。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Key Timeline</span><span class="lang-zh">重要時間線</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium w-24 shrink-0">Aug 2023</div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-4 flex-1">
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <span class="lang-en">HashKey, OSL become first licensed VATPs</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">HashKey、OSL成為首批licensed VATPs</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium w-24 shrink-0">May 2024</div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-4 flex-1">
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <span class="lang-en">Stablecoin ordinance passed</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">穩定幣條例通過</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium w-24 shrink-0">Oct 2025</div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-4 flex-1">
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <span class="lang-en">e-HKD Phase 2 completed</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">e-HKD第2階段完成</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium w-24 shrink-0">Apr 2025</div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-4 flex-1">
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <span class="lang-en">SFC greenlit staking for licensed VATPs</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">SFC批准持牌VATP提供staking服務</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium w-24 shrink-0">Feb 2026</div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-4 flex-1">
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <span class="lang-en">12 VATPs licensed, family office digital asset tax concession effective</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">12間VATP獲牌、Family office digital asset稅務優惠生效</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-cyan-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Learn about HK regulation details</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">了解HK監管詳情</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
